Package suncertify.protocol

Provides interfaces and classes for working with Subcontractor objects and the SubcontractorCommand protocol.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Subcontractor The Subcontractor interface defines the methods for operating on a subcontractor.
SubcontractorCommand The SubcontractorCommand interface defines methods for invoking the commands that operate on subcontractors.
 

Class Summary
SubcontractorCommandImpl The SubcontractorCommandImpl class implements the SubcontractorCommand interface and uses an instance of the Data class (that implements the DB interface) to access its data store.
SubcontractorImpl The SubcontractorImpl class implements the Subcontractor interface.
 

Exception Summary
SubcontractorNotAvailableException Instances of the SubcontractorNotAvailableException class are thrown to indicate that the Subcontractor is not available for booking.
SubcontractorNotFoundException Instances of the SubcontractorNotFoundException class are thrown to indicate that the requested Subcontractor does not exist.
 

Package suncertify.protocol Description

Provides interfaces and classes for working with Subcontractor objects and the SubcontractorCommand protocol.
